cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with text detection and recognition in natural scene images using convolutional recurrent neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves natural language processing, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of neural networks for text recognition and detection also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
